1. *Vatra* je osetljiva na vetar. (Fire is sensitive to wind.)
2. Deca su se igrala oko *vatre*. (The children were playing around the fire.)
3. *Vatru* smo uspeli da ugase. (We managed to put out the fire.)
4. On je prigrlio *vatru*. (He embraced the fire.)
5. Ona je u≈æivala u toploti *vatre*. (She enjoyed the warmth of the fire.)
6. *Vatre* nema u ovom delu sveta. (There is no fire in this part of the world.)
7. Plamen *vatre* se uvek predstavlja kao znak nade. (The flame of fire is always presented as a sign of hope.)
8. On je umro od izlaganja *vatri*. (He died from exposure to fire.)